{"tid":1021259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛星圖片顯示西藏集中營　印媒揭中共謊言","createTime":"2019-02-14T06:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T05:46:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1e21f47c1dc02fe474fe8b6c22435b6e17ded8b9","tid":1021259,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/106416/____1_@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F106416%2F____1_%401200x1200.jpg&h=0058812f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">印度The Print網站以衛星圖片證實西藏設有「再教育營」，至少有3個這種設施被辨識出來。（網絡圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儘管中共矢口否認新疆或西藏地區有「再教育營」的存在，但印度媒體援引衛星圖片揭穿其謊言。這些衛星圖片顯示，西藏目前至少有3個類似前蘇聯時代集中營的「再教育營」正在興建。<br />\n<br />\n印度The Print網站去年8月曾援引衛星圖片證實，新疆興建了多座「再教育營」用以迫害維族人，而美國和聯合國的報告也指出這種「再教育營」確實存在。<br />\n<br />\n如今，該網站再度引用衛星圖片說，西藏目前至少有3個「再教育營」正在興建。該地區的宗教、語言和文化也面臨中共的嚴厲監控與打壓。<br />\n<br />\n西藏活動人士指出，中共自1958年統治西藏以來，一直箝制當地的宗教活動。在上個世紀80年代中期，大約有6,254座寺廟被拆毀。<br />\n<br />\n現在，西藏的寺院依中式建築的樣式重建或整修。新建的寺院通常離城鎮很遠，顯然是為了避開人群。<br />\n<br />\n這些寺院疑為用來對不屈服於中共的僧侶進行「再教育」的設施，亦即所謂的「再教育營」。<br />\n<br />\n至少有3個這種設施經由衛星圖片被辨識出來。這些設施都還在興建中，而且設有高牆。內圈的高牆比外圈的高，在角落有警衛看守。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音去年曾引述一名藏族僧人的證言說，他曾在這樣的「再教育營」待了4個月。他們被要求唱紅歌，並接受用漢語授課的政治和法律課程，不但要玷污達賴喇嘛，還要自我批評。<br />\n<br />\n這名僧人回憶，白天他們要在太陽下進行「軍訓」；晚上要開「文革式」的鬥爭會。除了被毆打之外，他們還會受到剝奪食物和睡眠的懲罰，甚至性侵害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-02-14/58348755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-02-14%2F58348755&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDuEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=9d54add6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-02-14/58348755</a>"},{"pid":"ed479ab5bc674a681730e2ec6a4705bfe1f3b1c2","tid":1021259,"uid":1672,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"納粹中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f84cfc3c7555c4b1e021bb44c191bf874ce1b57","tid":1021259,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"中国強調納稅是＂重中之重＂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858c562f0a903f7cbff977e89c23bc8ecad4f088","tid":1021259,"uid":119347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"Gulag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc76ee6907f71912d258b3cf5b1724c8ddb43b5","tid":1021259,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb82e2727039e68b2f1b8e594feba3a8238bbf8e","tid":1021259,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"聯合國已經廢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e209398926a6225c580ff4fa1a161c489066e7","tid":1021259,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb82e2727039e68b2f1b8e594feba3a8238bbf8e","tid":1021259,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"聯合國已經廢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"幾時有用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e773f339d3a6a931bd6ef8d312d2d2fed6977c","tid":1021259,"uid":81783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港好快都會有依一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5123215549921610a5c9046e72c79d30e2a743","tid":1021259,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e209398926a6225c580ff4fa1a161c489066e7","tid":1021259,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb82e2727039e68b2f1b8e594feba3a8238bbf8e","tid":1021259,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":